{"tid":1351450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每人推10個721上環post才睡覺","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T17:45:32.000Z","uid":278712,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1e95518309868fa089dba090b4af9e773c50a415","tid":1351450,"uid":278712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"元朗和上環的事件同樣重要，而且根源都是一樣，不過暫時上環的post較少，要平衡一下。<br />\n還有6月9日：100萬人上街，政府無視<br />\n6月12日：開槍打頭、催淚彈、中信<br />\n6月14日：黃雨衣義士<br />\n6月16日：200萬人<br />\n7月1日：立法會死士<br />\n上水跳橋、沙田新都城、TVB不公正報導，還有很多很多，不應該忘記，首先自己不要忘記，互相提醒，努力會像投票一樣，到了某個程度才會見到結果。"},{"pid":"205a2b9032bc483b441997778bfd7f634dbf10d7","tid":1351450,"uid":278712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"沙田是新城市"},{"pid":"379c7a95764e357e69f3d2e9817075a723702dea","tid":1351450,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:30:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed9b9296979617561fcc5f82c959072e03384e04","tid":1351450,"uid":286087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:32:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f285c55b958c0cbadf0f8ed0638f69765d63de15","tid":1351450,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23636598a21a29469833f4bd01f1bd72b7d4755d","tid":1351450,"uid":145884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:53:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"604909fa0ba6678c600ed372d3b67bcb20746362","tid":1351450,"uid":278712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"有同伴說焦點變得模糊。<br />\n其實就算是一間小公司，也不會只有一個簡單目標，一定是有長遠、有短期、有想做的、有不想做但必須先處理的各種事情等等。<br />\n最重要是自己心裏明白，每天思考，互相鼓勵和提醒。"},{"pid":"68e2571d133a68d9cd9d1e02e5364dcfb0bb9096","tid":1351450,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef4b9b93633e4b733ad730